entity_name: NEO25 M/C Ultra High Speed Camera 25,000fps@1280x1024
description:
High-sensitivity & ultra-high-speed camera utilizes a new generation of backside illumination sensors to enhance the capture efficiency of incident photons, enabling transient image capture within extremely short exposure times. This is suitable for ultra-high-speed applications.

Model: NEO 25M/C
Sensor: BSI CMOS
Max Resolution: 1280x1024
Full Frame Rate: 25000fps
Shutter: Global Shutter
Min Exposure Time: 150ns
PIV Cross Frame: 250ns
RAM: 320GB
Support Auto Exposure
Support EDR
Support Record Button

Video Interface: SDI
Input: 3.3/5V TTL
Output: 5V TTL
Time Input Interface: DC IRIG B
Control Interface: RS422 Reserved
Trigger Input: Pulse trigger signal
IO: I Output Interface Reserved, Customizable

Mount: F Port, C/EF Port Options
